OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning perhaps with
OL,6,Fsome light rain near the Norfolk
OL,7,Fcoast. Cloud breaking through the late
OL,8,Fmorning and afternoon with some sunny
OL,9,Fspells developing. Winds mainly light
OL,10,Fand variable.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCoastal cloud will move
OL,13,Finland giving a cloudy but dry evening
OL,14,Facross the region. Winds light and
OL,15,Fvariable but breezy along the coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA cloudy and dry start to the
OL,18,Fday, sunny spells start to develop
OL,19,Fduring the afternoon with clear skies
OL,20,Fovernight. Winds remain light and
OL,21,Fbreezy along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
