OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FStaying predominantly dry with
OL,7,Fvariable amounts of cloud and some
OL,8,Fclear or sunny spells, just a small
OL,9,Fchance of isolated showers. Winds
OL,10,Flight. Temperatures generally above
OL,11,Faverage.
